This paper deals with multimodal translation, which involves both natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, since the paper deals with multimodal data, it could also be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
